OL,5, Struggling high-cost lender Amigo has  
OL,6, said it will halt all lending and wind 
OL,7, down its business after failing to     
OL,8, raise extra funds from investors.      
OL,10,FIts failure has left more than 200,000 
OL,11,Fcustomers in the dark over compensation
OL,12,Fthey will receive for mis-sold         
OL,13,Fproducts, a debt expert said.          
OL,15,FAmigo had been sanctioned by regulators
OL,16,Ffor insufficient affordability checks  
OL,17,Fon the people it lent to.              
OL,19,FIt had been trying to raise money to   
OL,20,Fhelp pay the compensation owed.        
